"""
        Test that a TypeError is raised when an invalid value is used to set
        the attributes of an ObjectDefaults structure.
        """
kwargs = {'attributes': 0}
self.assertRaisesRegex(TypeError,
    'Attributes must be an Attributes structure.', objects.ObjectDefaults,
    **kwargs)
args = objects.ObjectDefaults(), 'attributes', 0
self.assertRaisesRegex(TypeError,
    'Attributes must be an Attributes structure.', setattr, *args)
